      "span_text": "If ω (k 0 ) = 0, diffusive mixing of the local wave number cannot be expected: instead, depending on the sign of ω (k 0 )(k + − k − ), we expect that q(x, t) evolves either as a stable viscous shock or as an approximate rarefaction wave [CITATION_1] ."
